PrecisAppointment of MILES RICHARDSON, of Haida Gwaii, British Columbia, as a British Columbia Treaty Commissioner, to hold office during pleasure commencing on the latest date of the present Order in Council, the Order issued by the Provincial Government and the Resolution of the First Nations Summit, and ending on the earlier of April 13, 1997, or the date on which the appointment is revoked by resolution of the Summit.
